{"tid":618523,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"上次搭地鐵見到Cathxxxxx Ng","createTime":"2018-04-06T01:31:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T12:00:49.000Z","uid":5499,"like":68,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"dcdaf19ea108bda55e2d492d62a28e14b6a01f1e","tid":618523,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T01:31:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小弟<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中年大叔<br />\nCathxxxx Ng<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大肚婆，你坐啦，我d廢中企下就得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食屎啦你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你唔想坐都唔洗咁講野下話<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呀叔，條撚樣唔係大肚婆呀，係大肚腩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n這時，Cathxxxx Ng 便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，「大肚腩也算大肚&hellip;&hellip;肚腩！&hellip;&hellip;肥婆的事，你們懂個屁？」接連便是難懂的話，什麼「肥西固窮」，什麼「者乎」之類，引得衆人都鬨笑起來：地鐵內外充滿了快活的空氣。"},{"pid":"9561e5f85c11d3f8d6d30de0310993f8100dff50","tid":618523,"uid":172915,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T01:32:23.000Z","msg":"哈哈！笑死我啦！"},{"pid":"a92968dcc7ed2464fd4088c1103f4e5a0acb08f5","tid":618523,"uid":74171,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T01:37:34.000Z","msg":"你睇佢個post 似乎有輕度語癌，應該唔會講咩「者乎」之類嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ea814ae28e27744cba050d92b5f23882f895b1","tid":618523,"uid":5499,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a92968dcc7ed2464fd4088c1103f4e5a0acb08f5","tid":618523,"uid":74171,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-0